<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>식물 하나를 키우는 데는 온 학교가 필요하다</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      color-scheme: light;
      --bg: #eef9ef;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --surface-strong: #f3fff3;
      --text: #1f3d1f;
      --muted: #5c6d5c;
      --accent: #6aa95c;
      --accent-strong: #3b7c3b;
      --border: rgba(90, 117, 90, 0.15);
      --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(47, 86, 47, 0.12);
      --radius: 28px;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #f6fff2 0%, var(--bg) 45%, #d9f2d4 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    button,
    input,
    textarea,
    a {
      font: inherit;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .loader-screen {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f4fbf4 0%, #cfeacc 100%);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      z-index: 9999;
    }

    .loader-card {
      width: min(92vw, 420px);
      padding: 36px 28px;
      border-radius: 32px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      border: 1px solid rgba(101, 150, 101, 0.18);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(41, 112, 41, 0.14);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .loader-card h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: var(--accent-strong);
    }

    .loader-text {
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .hidden {
      display: none !important;
    }

    .emoji-background {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      overflow: hidden;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .emoji-background span {
      position: absolute;
      opacity: 0.45;
      pointer-events: none;
      user-select: none;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .emoji-background span.float {
      animation: float 14s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .emoji-background span.drift {
      animation: drift 18s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
      50% { transform: translate(8px, -18px); }
    }

    @keyframes drift {
      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
      50% { transform: translate(18px, 6px); }
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      max-width: 1240px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 30px 28px 60px;
    }

    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 10px 0 30px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(106, 169, 92, 0.12);
      color: var(--accent-strong);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .topbar h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 3.6rem);
      line-height: 1.02;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .topbar p {
      margin-top: 18px;
      max-width: 720px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .topnav {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    .topnav a {
      padding: 10px 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(106, 169, 92, 0.14);
      color: var(--accent-strong);
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
    }

    .topnav a:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      background: rgba(106, 169, 92, 0.2);
    }

    .hero-section {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 32px;
      align-items: stretch;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: #366833;
      background: rgba(106, 169, 92, 0.12);
      font-weight: 700;
      width: fit-content;
    }

    .hero-copy h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 4vw, 4rem);
      line-height: 1.02;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
    }

    .hero-copy p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 620px;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .button {
      padding: 16px 28px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }

    .button-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6aa95c, #3b7c3b);
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(45, 96, 39, 0.2);
    }

    .button-secondary {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      color: var(--accent-strong);
      border: 1px solid rgba(106, 169, 92, 0.2);
    }

    .button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .hero-card {
      min-height: 620px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .plant-card {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f9fff9 0%, #eefff1 100%);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 26px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-rows: auto 1fr auto;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .plant-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .plant-header .card-label {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--accent-strong);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .plant-header h3 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-top: 6px;
      color: #2f5b2f;
    }

    .status-chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(106, 169, 92, 0.16);
      color: var(--accent-strong);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .plant-sprite {
      min-height: 380px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #f6fff5 0%, #e3f7df 45%, #daf2d3 100%);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 28px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(82, 146, 82, 0.15);
    }

    .plant-note {
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .status-grid {
      margin: 40px 0 10px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .status-card {
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid rgba(95, 142, 95, 0.14);
      padding: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(66, 122, 66, 0.08);
    }

    .status-card p {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .status-card strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: var(--accent-strong);
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    section {
      margin-top: 50px;
    }

    .section-header {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      max-width: 720px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .section-header span {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--accent-strong);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
    }

    .section-header p {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.9;
      max-width: 640px;
    }

    .actions {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .care-btn {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid rgba(106, 169, 92, 0.2);
      color: var(--text);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 18px 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
      min-height: 82px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .care-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      border-color: rgba(106, 169, 92, 0.4);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 34px rgba(62, 110, 62, 0.12);
    }

    .message-area {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.7fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    textarea {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 116px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(96, 146, 96, 0.22);
      padding: 18px;
      resize: none;
      background: #fbfff9;
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    #sendMsg {
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: none;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6aa95c, #3b7c3b);
      color: white;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 18px 24px;
      align-self: flex-end;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }

    #sendMsg:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 34px rgba(62, 110, 62, 0.18);
    }

    .messages {
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .msg-card {
      padding: 22px;
      background: #fbfff9;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(96, 146, 96, 0.18);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(45, 93, 45, 0.08);
      min-height: 120px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .msg-card div:first-child {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .msg-card small {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .logs-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .logs-list li {
      padding: 18px 20px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid rgba(106, 169, 92, 0.12);
      color: var(--text);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(44, 89, 44, 0.08);
    }

    .growth-card {
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fbfff9 0%, #e7f9e4 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(106, 169, 92, 0.18);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 32px;
    }

    .growth-card h3 {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: #3f6e3f;
    }

    .growth-card p {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.9;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .growth-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(106, 169, 92, 0.14);
      color: var(--accent-strong);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .effect-layer {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .sparkle {
      position: absolute;
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95) 0%, rgba(144, 218, 144, 0.8) 50%, transparent 100%);
      opacity: 0;
      transform: scale(0.5);
      animation: spark 900ms ease-out forwards;
    }

    @keyframes spark {
      0% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) scale(0.6); }
      100% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-80px) scale(1.4); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 1080px) {
      .hero-section {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .status-grid,
      .actions,
      .message-area,
      .messages {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .message-area {
        align-items: stretch;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .page {
        padding: 20px 18px 40px;
      }

      .topbar {
        display: block;
      }

      .topnav {
        justify-content: flex-start;
      }

      .hero-copy h2 {
        font-size: 2.4rem;
      }

      .plant-card {
        padding: 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="loader-screen" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="loader-card">
      <h1>함께 자라는 식물 다마고치</h1>
      <p class="loader-text">잠시만 기다려주세요...</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="emoji-background" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <main class="page container hidden">
    <section class="topbar">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">QR 참여형 식물 돌봄</span>
        <h1>식물 하나를 키우는 데는 온 학교가 필요하다</h1>
        <p>물·햇빛·관찰·응원이 모여서 학교 식물을 함께 키우는 따뜻한 디지털 다마고치입니다.</p>
      </div>
      <nav class="topnav">
        <a href="#care">돌봄하기</a>
        <a href="#memory">응원 메시지</a>
        <a href="#logs">돌봄 흔적</a>
        <a href="#growth">성장 보기</a>
      </nav>
    </section>

    <section class="hero-section">
      <article class="hero-copy">
        <div class="badge">여러 참여자가 함께 돌보는 식물</div>
        <h2>QR을 통해 언제든 참여하고,<br>따뜻한 관심을 식물에 남겨요.</h2>
        <p>익명으로 참여할 수 있는 돌봄 버튼과 응원 메시지로, 식물의 하루를 함께 만들어주세요.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="#care" class="button button-primary">돌봄하러 가기</a>
          <a href="#memory" class="button button-secondary">응원 남기기</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="hero-card">
        <div class="plant-card">
          <div class="plant-header">
            <div>
              <p class="card-label">식물 친구</p>
              <h3>초록이</h3>
            </div>
            <span class="status-chip">익명 참여형</span>
          </div>

          <div id="plantSprite" class="plant-sprite" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 120 120" width="220" height="220" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <defs>
                <filter id="soft" x="-20%" y="-20%" width="140%" height="140%">
                  <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="1.2" />
                </filter>
              </defs>
              <rect width="120" height="120" rx="16" fill="#f6fff6" />
              <g transform="translate(10,18)">
                <ellipse cx="50" cy="80" rx="36" ry="12" fill="#c9a27a" />
                <rect x="30" y="48" width="40" height="36" rx="6" fill="#e6caa7" />
                <g id="leaves" fill="#4caf50" filter="url(#soft)">
                  <ellipse cx="50" cy="36" rx="30" ry="14" />
                  <ellipse cx="36" cy="26" rx="18" ry="8" transform="rotate(-20 36 26)" />
                  <ellipse cx="64" cy="26" rx="18" ry="8" transform="rotate(20 64 26)" />
                </g>
                <circle id="eyeL" cx="44" cy="32" r="2.5" fill="#173a18" />
                <circle id="eyeR" cx="56" cy="32" r="2.5" fill="#173a18" />
              </g>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <p class="plant-note">식물을 살피는 행동을 선택하면, 오늘의 관심 수와 메시지가 함께 쌓입니다.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="status-grid">
      <article class="status-card">
        <p>함께 자란 시간</p>
        <strong id="growTime">--일 --시간</strong>
      </article>
      <article class="status-card">
        <p>마지막 돌봄</p>
        <strong id="lastCare">--시간</strong>
      </article>
      <article class="status-card">
        <p>오늘 받은 관심</p>
        <strong id="todayCount">0</strong>
      </article>
      <article class="status-card">
        <p>남겨진 마음</p>
        <strong id="messageCount">0</strong>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section id="care">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span>CARE</span>
        <h2>간단한 돌봄 버튼으로 참여하기</h2>
        <p>흙, 햇빛, 잎 관찰, 새 변화 발견 중 하나를 선택하면 오늘의 식물 상태가 기록됩니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="actions">
        <button class="care-btn" data-type="soil">흙 확인했어요</button>
        <button class="care-btn" data-type="sunlight">햇빛 확인했어요</button>
        <button class="care-btn" data-type="leaf">잎을 관찰했어요</button>
        <button class="care-btn" data-type="new">새 변화를 발견했어요</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="memory">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span>MEMORY</span>
        <h2>응원 메시지 잎사귀</h2>
        <p>30자 이내의 짧은 응원 메시지를 남겨주세요. 익명으로 식물에게 마음을 보낼 수 있어요.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="message-area">
        <textarea id="msgInput" maxlength="30" placeholder="응원 메시지를 30자 이내로 남겨주세요." rows="4"></textarea>
        <button id="sendMsg">마음 남기기</button>
      </div>
      <div id="messages" class="messages"></div>
    </section>

    <section id="logs">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span>LOGS</span>
        <h2>오늘의 돌봄 흔적</h2>
        <p>익명 참여자들이 남긴 돌봄 기록이 시간 순으로 쌓입니다.</p>
      </div>
      <ul id="logsList" class="logs-list"></ul>
    </section>

    <section id="growth">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span>GROWTH</span>
        <h2>작은 관심이 큰 성장을 만듭니다</h2>
        <p>식물은 하루하루의 관심을 모아 천천히 자라요. 여러분의 기록이 바로 성장의 증거입니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="growth-card">
        <h3>오늘의 성장 기록</h3>
        <p>오늘까지 모인 돌봄 행동과 응원이 식물의 하루를 따뜻하게 채우고 있습니다.</p>
        <div class="growth-pill">총 돌봄 기록 <strong id="careCount">0</strong>개</div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <div id="effectLayer" class="effect-layer" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <script src="app.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
